    <example>
      <statement>
        <p>
          This example examines the relationship between a county's population change from 2010 to 2017 and median household income,
          which is visualized as a scatterplot in <xref ref="pop_change_v_med_income">Figure</xref>.
          Are these variables associated?
        </p>
      </statement>
      <answer>
        <p>
          The larger the median household income for a county,
          the higher the population growth observed for the county.
          While this trend isn't true for every county,
          the trend in the plot is evident.
          Since there is some relationship between the variables,
          they are associated.
        </p>
      </answer>
    </example>
    <p>
      \end{example}
    </p>
